00:00:28.860 --> 00:00:32.595
But the short list, obviously,
is Anita Sarkeesian's video

00:00:32.595 --> 00:00:36.000
and her being forced to leave
her home because of threats

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:37.140
of violence.

00:00:37.140 --> 00:00:39.960
Zoe Quinn, another
game developer,

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:44.310
who had a former, past--
whatever-- someone

00:00:44.310 --> 00:00:46.630
write some nasty things
about her on the internet,

00:00:46.630 --> 00:00:50.910
and her being attacked
